                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Auto-Scheduling Deep Dive -->
<section id="scheduling" class="scheduling-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header text-center">
            <span class="section-badge">Intelligent Scheduling</span>
            <h2>Evolutionary algorithms<br /><span class="gradient-text">meet workforce planning</span></h2>
            <p class="section-description">
                Klacks doesn't just randomly assign shifts. It models each employee as an autonomous agent
                and runs an evolutionary optimization &mdash; testing hundreds of scenarios to find the best possible schedule.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">01</div>
                    <h4>Warm Start</h4>
                    <p>Greedy seeding assigns obvious matches first. Random scenarios fill the rest. 50+ initial plans generated.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">02</div>
                    <h4>Evolution</h4>
                    <p>Block crossover recombines the best plans day-by-day. Heuristic mutations swap, repair, and optimize.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">03</div>
                    <h4>Fitness Check</h4>
                    <p>Every plan is scored against hard constraints (legal limits) and soft constraints (preferences, fairness).</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">04</div>
                    <h4>Result</h4>
                    <p>After 200 generations: an optimized schedule achieving up to 95% fitness. Delivered in under 15 seconds.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="scheduling-rules text-center mt-5">
            <h4>Configurable Scheduling Rules</h4>
            <div class="rules-grid">
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Max Daily Hours</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-calendar-week"></i> Max Work Days</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-bed"></i> Min Rest Period</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-moon"></i> Night Shift Limits</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Team Preferences</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Qualifications</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> Fair Distribution</div>
                <div class="rule-chip"><i class="fas fa-umbrella-beach"></i> Availability Windows</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

