                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="mini-feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-bell feature-mini-icon"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5>Real-Time Updates</h5>
                        <p>SignalR-powered live notifications. When someone edits a shift, everyone sees it instantly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="mini-feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-shield feature-mini-icon"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5>Enterprise Authentication</h5>
                        <p>OAuth2, OpenID Connect, LDAP sync, JWT tokens. Single sign-on with your existing identity provider.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="mini-feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-sitemap feature-mini-icon"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5>Group Hierarchy</h5>
                        <p>Nested groups with visibility control. Departments, teams, locations &mdash; any structure you need.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="mini-feature">
                    <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave feature-mini-icon"></i>
                    <div>
                        <h5>Expense Tracking</h5>
                        <p>Track tax-liable expenses and non-taxable compensation at shift and work level. Contract management built in.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

